Description
Today we start as Saigon_Zoo and do a canal run . To avoid that we all start at the same time but finish at different times , we will base the training duration on time . The drill is a 60 minutes run . Follow the route below and after 30 minutes turn back . The total route plotted is 11.4km ( go and come back ) . Faster runners may do the full route whereas others may just be doing 7km .
Today should be an easy run .
Schedule
05 : 30 ; 15 minutes gathering and warm up ; make sure to do your own warm up
5 : 45AM Sharp we start running .
To avoid that people wait a long time in the morning , we will start immediately at 5 : 45AM . In case you didn ' t arrive yet , please follow the route and we will meet you on the route . Do however send a message if you are later .
Route
The full route is : http : / / ridewithgps.com/routes/10865302
( Remember : it is a 60 minutes run so most likely you will turn back earlier then doing the full route ) .
